      "description": "Bulk RNA-seq preprocessing pipeline using nf-core/rnaseq v3.22.2 with the STAR-Salmon workflow. Takes raw paired-end FASTQ files, performs quality control (FastQC, TrimGalore), alignment (STAR), quantification (Salmon), and generates a comprehensive MultiQC report. iGenomes is disabled by default; users provide their own reference FASTA and GTF files.",
